{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As far as the Jewish life-- well, the few Jewish people that were left were really concentrating on my-- my aunt's house because she opened the hotel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whoever was coming really knew her, I mean, that came to the hotel and stayed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we heard stories from all over the place and from everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I really didn't have much to do with the Poles, except I went to school in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I went as Eva Najnudel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under my name, under-- as a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came into class, and all of a sudden, there were a few other Jewish kids there in class.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Poles started picking up on them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[POLISH] and [POLISH] and all kinds of names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it really got to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, I-- I decided that I'm not going to be a Jew, because I don't want anybody picking on me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started going to religion, to Catholic religion, and I started pray in class, and I tried to behave-- not with my name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was hard, but I did it anyhow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Until Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt was very religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for Rosh Hashanah, she said, you're not going to school today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, when I came back to school the next day, my teacher says to me, and where are you yesterday?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to her, well, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't feeling well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in front of the whole class, she says, well, wasn't that the Jewish holiday yesterday?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
